Program: Outlook
Title: The Gambia Under Threat by Rising Sea Levels
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrgn
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The disappearing beaches in The Gambia as sea levels rise and the capital Banjul is under threat. Also, 'Yugo-nostalgia' and the shared common culture of the former Yugoslavia countries; Outlook follows one sitar from it's production in Delhi to Southall, West London and finally, how will future generations remember us? Presented by Fred Dove. Show less